Van Rooyen ma ọ bụ Van Rooijen (pronunciation Dutch: [vɑn ʼroːjɵn]) bụ aha nna Afrikaans na Dutch toponymic
"Rooij" ma ọ bụ "Roij" bụ okwu obodo maka ọtụtụ obodo na-ejedebe na "rode" ma ọ bụ "roij", dị ka Nistelrode, Sint-Oedenrode, Stramproy na Wanroij
